usted fire hydrant and this pleases both the Americans and Chinese money vampires alike. When Elon speaks his autistic stutter breaks words in half. He pauses like his brain is a pinball machine ding dinging points. Jokes fall out his mouth like broken teeth but without the blood flavor. For Musk even a whisper of poonani and he's on the hunt. Stalking nightclub floors, nostrils flaring, pelvis grinding. He throws benjamins at the girls until they stick like flies in shit. His rival is Mark Zuckerberg, the alien in manflesh who makes websites. It is a hate thing deep as marrow. Musk craves to crack Zuck open like a spoiled egg and eat his stinking yolk. He pictures the two of them naked in Rome, sword to sword, cock to cock. He wants to paint the old stone seats new with heartsblood in the high sun.\\n\\nMusk's brain vibrates, atoms splitting, quarks decaying into gibberish particles. He's got cash and cars and star yachts and dreams of big rockets. Holes that need filling like them tunnels under LA. Ain't no cavity safe from Elon's probing. The ladies line up, hypnotized by the musk of money. He plucks em like low-hanging fruit and spits out the seeds. His blood boils at the mention of that alien fuck in a skin suit. The Zuckerberg. Can't cuck the Zuck, they say. Yeah, fuck that. Chrome dome with eyes like pissholes in snow. Wants to crack that bulbous head like a week-old watermelon. Wants to queeze the lizard juice out of his nuts and make a cocktail garnished with silicon and scales.\\n</elon>\",\"enabled\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"case_sensitive\":false,\"priority\":10,\"id\":5,\"comment\":\"Elon Musk\",\"selective\":true,\"constant\":false,\"position\":\"before_char\",\"extensions\":{\"role\":0,\"depth\":4,\"group\":\"\",\"linked\":false,\"weight\":10,\"addMemo\":true,\"embedded\":true,\"position\":0,\"scan_depth\":null,\"vectorized\":false,\"probability\":100,\"displayIndex\":1,\"group_weight\":100,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"display_index\":4,\"case_sensi